At a [ORG CRP] meeting on March 21 , 1971 , it was agreed to spend $250,000 on " intelligence gathering " on the [ORG Democratic Party] . 
[PER Colson] and [PER John Ehrlichman] appointed [PER E. Howard Hunt] to the [LOC White House] Special Operations Unit ( the so-called " Plumbers " ) which had been organized to stop leaks in the [PER Nixon] administration . 
[PER Hunt] headed up the [MISC Plumbers'] burglary of [ORG Pentagon] Papers-leaker [PER Daniel Ellsberg] 's psychiatrist 's office in September 1971 . 
[LOC The Pentagon] Papers were military documents about the [MISC Vietnam War] which helped increase opposition to the war . 
[PER Colson] hoped that revelations about [PER Ellsberg] could be used to discredit the [MISC anti-Vietnam War] cause . 
